'''Death dice''' was presumably, a kind of gambling game that [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] and [[Jinkins]] often played. The rules of the game are unknown. Nym was supposedly good at the game, or was a bit of a cheater as sometimes Jinkins accused Nym of cheating going as far as challenging him to a dogfight.

